    <div class="project-section">
        <div class="project-details">
            <div class="project-info">
                <div class="project-name">Clean Energy</div>
                <div class="project-description">
                    <div class="initial-solutions">
                        <p>Develop Renewable Energy Sources: Invest in and promote the development of renewable energy
                            sources such as solar, wind, hydro, and geothermal power. These sources are sustainable and
                            produce little to no greenhouse gas emissions, making them crucial for reducing the carbon
                            footprint and combating climate change.</p>
                        <p>Promote Energy Efficiency and Conservation: Encourage the adoption of energy-efficient
                            technologies and practices. This includes using LED lighting, energy-efficient appliances,
                            and smart home systems that optimize energy use. Conservation efforts, such as turning off
                            lights and appliances when not in use, also play a significant role in reducing energy
                            consumption.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="moreSolutionsEnergy" class="more-solutions-hidden">
                        <p>Invest in Smart Grid Technology: Implement smart grid technology to enhance the efficiency
                            and reliability of the electricity grid. Smart grids use digital communication technology to
                            detect and respond to local changes in usage, reducing energy waste and improving the
                            integration of renewable energy sources..</p>
                        <p>Encourage the Use of Electric Vehicles: Support the transition to electric vehicles (EVs) by
                            providing incentives for EV purchases and investing in charging infrastructure. EVs produce
                            zero tailpipe emissions and, when powered by renewable energy, offer a sustainable
                            alternative to traditional fossil fuel-powered vehicles.</p>
                        <p>Implement energy storage solutions to store excess energy generated by renewable sources.</p>
                        <p>Support community energy projects like solar co-ops and wind farms to empower communities.
                        </p>
                        <p>Promote green building standards to encourage the construction of energy-efficient buildings.
                        </p>
                        <p>Advocate for government policies and incentives that support the adoption of clean energy.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="view-project">
