    <div class="project-section">
        <img class="project-image" src="/images/CleanWater.jpeg" alt="Clean Water">
        <div class="project-details">
            <div class="project-info">
                <div class="project-name">Access to Water & Sanitation</div>
                <div class="project-description">
                    <div class="initial-solutions">
                        <p>Ensure Access to Clean Water for All: Implement programs that provide clean and safe drinking
                            water to all communities, especially in rural and underdeveloped areas. This can be achieved
                            through the construction of wells, rainwater harvesting systems, and the installation of
                            water purification technologies.</p>
                        <p>Promote Water Conservation Practices: Educate communities on the importance of water
                            conservation and implement practices to reduce water waste. This includes using
                            water-efficient fixtures, fixing leaks promptly, and encouraging behaviors such as turning
                            off taps while brushing teeth and taking shorter showers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="moreSolutionsWater" class="more-solutions-hidden">
                        <p>Improve Wastewater Treatment Infrastructure: Invest in modernizing and expanding wastewater
                            treatment facilities to ensure that sewage and industrial waste are properly treated before
                            being released into the environment. This helps to protect water sources from contamination
                            and supports overall public health.
                        </p>
                        <p>Support community-led sanitation projects to empower local communities in managing their own
                            sanitation systems.</p>
                        <p>Implement Integrated Water Resource Management (IWRM) for sustainable management of water
                            resources.</p>
                        <p>Enhance rainwater harvesting techniques to reduce reliance on conventional water sources.</p>
                        <p>Develop emergency water supply systems to ensure access to clean water during natural
                            disasters.</p>
                        <p>Advocate for policy reforms and investment in water and sanitation infrastructure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="view-project">
                <button id="viewMoreButtonWater">View More</button>
